<i>adverb</i>: 찌르릉 [찌르릉], 딩동 [딩동] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>adverb</i><br>
<dt>찌르릉 [찌르릉]</dt><br>
<dd>ring; ding-dong</dd><br>
<dd>초인종이나 전화벨 등이 울리는 소리.</dd><br>
<dd>A word used to describe the sound made when a doorbell, telephone, etc., rings.</dd><br>
<dt>딩동 [딩동]</dt><br>
<dd>ding-dong</dd><br>
<dd>초인종 등의 벨이 울리는 소리.</dd><br>
<dd>A word imitating the sound made by bells including a doorbell.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>